::Stratus::

Stratus runs down the hallway, heading out of the base when he sees
Slaugher up ahead, and a large hand beyond him. He screeches to a
halt, firing two pods that slide over the ground toward Slaugher.

"Sir, the way's blocked by the intruder. I'll go through him but he
might delay me a bit." he says over the comm to Megatron, running
forward as the pods launch themselves at Slaughter, releasing vines
to trap him.
